title: IntroScript
tags:
---
Srushti: Hello Player. My name is Srushti, and these are my friends, Katia and Laxmi. Welcome to this experience. #line:Srushti01
Srushti: In this experience, you are an Eco Warrior who has embarked on a quest to save the environment. #line:Srushti11
Srushti: Each level gives you a task to enhance your knowledge about the environment, adverse effects of climate change and how to save it. #line:Srushti12
Srushti: After you complete each level, you will be able to move on to the next one. Dont worry, one of us will always be there to guide you. #line:Srushti13 
Srushti: Also, dont forget to read the controller instructions written around you.  #line:Srushti04 
Srushti: So! Are you ready to dive in to it?  Come on then! May you be the best Eco Warrior this world has ever seen! #line:Srushti14 
Srushti: Click on the start button to begin the first game. #line:Srushti06 
===

title: BeachSceneIntro
tags:
---
Srushti: Hello Player. My name is Srushti, Welcome to the last experience. In this experience, you will have to complete 2 tasks. #line:Srushti07 
Srushti: First, there will be objects falling which represent the things that are harmfull for the climate. You have to destroy them with the sword given.  #line:Srushti08 
Srushti: Second, you have to collect atleast 5 items, which are harmfull for the environment. These objects are scattered around the scene. #line:Srushti09 
Srushti: Okay then. Good Luck! You can now see the objects falling. You can begin your first task. #line:Srushti10 
===

