Laxmi: Hello Player. My name is Laxmi. Welcome to this quiz which I have created.  #line:Laxmi01 
Laxmi: Your task here is to answer the questions correctly regarding Beach pollution. Please read the information about beach pollution around you and answer the questions. #line:Laxmi02 
Laxmi: The board with questions is up ahead. Please walk closer to it when you are ready to start the quiz. #line:Laxmi03 
Laxmi: When you are done with the quiz, you can move onto the next level. Good Luck! #line:Laxmi04 
===

title:TreasureHuntSceneIntro
tags:
---
Katia: Hello Player. My name is Katia. Welcome to this experience which I have created.  #line:Katia01 
Katia: In this scene you will be doing a treasure hunt. I have hidden some items around the scene and you need to find them. These items can help us fight the adverse effects of climate change. #line:Katia02 
Katia: You can see what you have to collect from the pictures that are around you. Once you find the objects, you have to drop them in the box below the pictures. #line:Katia03 
Katia: Make sure to match the correct item with its picture otherwise you wont be able to finish this game. goodluck! #line:Katia04 

===